episodes.name: A Second First Impression
episodes.overview: Thirteen suitors arrive at a mansion anxiously awaiting to meet their Prince Charming. Robert, a gorgeous Atlanta-based interior designer, is the Prince Charming looking for the love of his life.

episodes.name: The Canary
episodes.overview: The guys head to the beach with Robert and two lucky suitors get to go on a date with Prince Charming.

episodes.name: Sensing a Connection
episodes.overview: The guys have two romantic group dates with Robert and drama overwhelms the mansion.

episodes.name: Appetite for Love
episodes.overview: Robert goes on a three course dinner date with three of the guys and someone is asked to give back their tie.

episodes.name: Man Behind the Mask
episodes.overview: Robert gets to know the guys deeper during a masquerade ball and friends are forced to choose.

episodes.name: What About Robert
episodes.overview: The remaining guys are put to the test to see which of them knows Robert best. Their patience is tested when two suitors find themselves having to share Robert on a romantic date. A shocking elimination leaves the house rattled.

episodes.name: A Family Affair
episodes.overview: The guys meet Robert's family and Robert is forced to make a tough decision at the black tie ceremony.

episodes.name: The Last Black Tie
episodes.overview: It's down to the final three and Robert is forced to make the tough decision to crown his prince charming.
